snippet.title: OHSU Confidential Advocacy
snippet.description: The OHSU Confidential Advocacy Program provides confidential support services to Oregon Health & Science University employees, students, and volunteers who have experienced any form of sexual misconduct or violence. Our educational videos are for healthcare providers as well as community-based, campus, and legal advocates and the overall OHSU community. Our therapy videos are especially for survivors of sexual misconduct or violence.
